OL,3,CNearly 200 babies from church-run
OL,4,Chomes buried in unmarked graves
OL,6,FAn investigation by ITV News has found
OL,7,Fthat nearly 200 babies are buried in
OL,8,Funmarked graves across England, amid
OL,9,Fallegations of neglect and poor
OL,10,Ftreatment at church run homes for
OL,11,Funmarried mothers in the 1950s, 60s
OL,12,Fand 70s.
OL,14,FBurials were often carried out in
OL,15,Fsecret, and without the knowledge of
OL,16,Ffamilies.
