OL,6,FEarlier this year our investigation
OL,7,Ffound that 45 babies who has died at a
OL,8,FChurch of England home in Cumbria are
OL,9,Fburied in a mass unmarked grave in the
OL,10,Ftown's cemetery.
OL,12,FSome families only found out the truth
OL,13,Fafter watching an ITV News report.
OL,14,FSince then, we have a found a
OL,15,Fdisturbing pattern of behaviour at
OL,16,Fother homes across England.
