OL,6,FOur evidence shows burials connected
OL,7,Fto at least four other Church of
OL,8,FEngland run homes, including 36
OL,9,Funmarked graves of babies born at the
OL,10,FWinchester Diocesan Maternity Home, 11
OL,11,Fgraves from St Saviour's in
OL,12,FNorthampton, 21 from Putnam House in
OL,13,FAylesbury and 2 connected to Sunnedon
OL,14,FHouse Maternity Home in Brentwood.
OL,16,FSome 24 infants died at a Salvation
OL,17,FArmy home in Newcastle called
OL,18,FHopedene, and are buried in unmarked
OL,19,Fgraves in four different cemeteries.
