OL,6,FDr Michael Lambert is a historian of
OL,7,Fthe welfare state at Lancaster
OL,8,FUniversity and has spent years
OL,9,Finvestigating these institutions.
OL,11,FHe told ITV News that unmarried
OL,12,Fmothers and their children were
OL,13,Ftreated like "second class citizens".
OL,15,F"Once babies were no longer seen as
OL,16,Fdesirable for adoption, they were
OL,17,Ftreated sub-standardly and weren't
OL,18,Fgiven the modern medical care which a
OL,19,F'legitimate child' at this time would
OL,20,Fhave had," he said.
