OL,6,FDr Lambert said the true number of
OL,7,Fmass unmarked graves from this period
OL,8,Fwas likely to be much higher. ITV News
OL,9,Fobtained records connected to eight
OL,10,Fhomes - there were more than 150
OL,11,Foperating across England for decades.
OL,13,FIn the decades after World War Two,
OL,14,Fbeing pregnant outside of wedlock was
OL,15,Fthe ultimate taboo. Mothers faced
OL,16,Fshame and stigma, and were pressured
OL,17,Finto putting their children up for
OL,18,Fadoption.
