OL,6,FMargaret Moore was born at St
OL,7,FPelagia's maternity home in the 1950s,
OL,8,Fwhich was run by Catholic nuns from
OL,9,Fthe Sisters of the Sacred Heart of
OL,10,FJesus and Mary.
OL,12,FShe described our findings as
OL,13,F"harrowing" and recounted her own
OL,14,F"bleak" start to life.
OL,16,F"I think those girls were looked on as
OL,17,Fthe dregs of society and their
OL,18,Foffspring, very much the same," she
OL,19,Fsaid.
