OL,6,F"On my medical records one of the
OL,7,Fthings that really hurt me was that
OL,8,Fthey said 'it can hear'. I was
OL,9,Fconsidered coloured, that was the
OL,10,Fphrase then, biracial now.
OL,12,F"So my race was commented on and I
OL,13,Fthink in the homes there was a tier
OL,14,Fsystem and I wasn't considered
OL,15,F'correct for adoption'."
