OL,6,FPart of her role was to try to support
OL,7,Fyoung, single mothers but she said
OL,8,Fthey often had very few options.
OL,10,F"The choices were still very limited.
OL,11,FThere was no proper income for them,
OL,12,Fand worst of all there was no
