OL,6,FThe campaign group Movement for an
OL,7,FAdoption Apology has written to the
OL,8,FPrime Minister Keir Starmer asking him
OL,9,Fto "do the right thing and issue a
OL,10,Fformal apology to all affected", and
OL,11,Fto "ensure that everyone who has been
OL,12,Ftraumatised receives the help they
OL,13,Fneed" - whether that be therapy,
OL,14,Fcounselling or improved post-adoption
OL,15,Fsupport.
OL,17,FThe Welsh and Scottish governments
OL,18,Fhave formally apologised for their
OL,19,Fpart in this scandal, but so far the
OL,20,FUK government has refused to do the
OL,21,Fsame.
